OL,5, Gary Lineker has been told to step back
OL,6, from presenting Match of the Day until 
OL,7, an agreement is reached on his social  
OL,8, media use, the BBC has said.           
OL,10,FIt follows an impartiality row over    
OL,11,Fcomments he made criticising the       
OL,12,Fgovernment's new asylum policy.        
OL,14,FThe BBC said it considered Lineker's   
OL,15,F"recent social media activity to be a  
OL,16,Fbreach of our guidelines".             
OL,18,FIt added he should "keep well away from
OL,19,Ftaking sides on party political issues 
OL,20,For political controversies".           
